A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Chapter 27 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, the "Georgia
2 Lottery for Education Act," so as to correct a reference; to provide for the application of the
3 provisions of the Georgia Administrative Procedure Act to certain provisions of the Code
4 relating to bona fide coin operated amusement machines; to provide for exemptions from the
5 Georgia Administrative Procedure Act regarding the Georgia Lottery Corporation for certain
6 matters not related to bona fide coin operated amusement machines; to provide for related
7 matters; to provide an effective date; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
8 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
9 SECTION 1.
10 Chapter 27 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, the "Georgia Lottery for
11 Education Act," is amended by revising paragraph (19) of subsection (a) of Code
12 Section 50-27-9, relating to general powers of the Georgia Lottery Corporation, as follows:
13 "(19) To adopt and amend such regulations, policies, and procedures as necessary to
14 carry out and implement its powers and duties, organize and operate the corporation,
15 regulate the conduct of lottery games in general, and any other matters necessary or
16 desirable for the efficient and effective operation of the lottery or the convenience of the
